00:20:16.600 --> 00:20:18.600
one obvious question
that pops up is:

00:20:18.600 --> 00:20:21.520
do the moderators do anything
to protect vulnerable users?

00:20:21.910 --> 00:20:23.380
Let's dig into that for a moment.

00:20:23.730 --> 00:20:25.200
First, the site states that

00:20:25.200 --> 00:20:27.200
only those of "sound mind"

00:20:27.200 --> 00:20:28.700
will be allowed to join the forum.

00:20:29.140 --> 00:20:30.410
Now, the term 'sound mind'

00:20:30.410 --> 00:20:32.600
is used to describe
a person's ability

00:20:32.600 --> 00:20:34.500
to reasonably understand
their surroundings

00:20:34.500 --> 00:20:36.400
and act rationally in
their own interest.

00:20:36.750 --> 00:20:38.650
It's an important thing
to determine in

00:20:38.650 --> 00:20:39.990
contentious legal situations,

00:20:39.990 --> 00:20:40.550
like

00:20:40.550 --> 00:20:42.890
when a person makes an
unusual change to their will

00:20:42.890 --> 00:20:44.620
or when they refuse
medical treatment.

00:20:44.930 --> 00:20:47.500
Did the person act in
sound mind at that moment,

00:20:47.500 --> 00:20:49.400
or were their actions
negatively influenced

00:20:49.400 --> 00:20:50.530
by something like

00:20:50.530 --> 00:20:51.330
coercion,

00:20:51.330 --> 00:20:52.078
bereavement,

00:20:52.080 --> 00:20:52.530
shock,

00:20:52.530 --> 00:20:53.660
extreme stress,

00:20:53.660 --> 00:20:54.400
psychosis,

00:20:54.400 --> 00:20:56.040
or other types of personal crisis?

00:20:56.740 --> 00:20:57.840
Second, on the forum's

00:20:57.840 --> 00:21:00.140
'Membership Requirements'
section, it states that

00:21:00.140 --> 00:21:03.060
no one with "intellectual
disabilities" can join either.

00:21:03.280 --> 00:21:05.340
Now, defining the term
'intellectual disability'

00:21:05.340 --> 00:21:06.870
is a tiny bit problematic here,

00:21:06.870 --> 00:21:08.380
because it's sometimes used

00:21:08.380 --> 00:21:09.860
way too broadly to refer to

00:21:09.860 --> 00:21:11.570
any kind of neurodivergence.

00:21:11.570 --> 00:21:13.150
I suspected the admins intended

00:21:13.150 --> 00:21:14.650
a much narrower definition

00:21:14.650 --> 00:21:17.970
to refer to those who are unable to
function independently without care.

00:21:18.260 --> 00:21:19.660
However, I can't be sure,

00:21:19.660 --> 00:21:20.920
so let's put that to one side.

00:21:21.250 --> 00:21:22.370
What's important is that

00:21:22.370 --> 00:21:23.810
by placing this rule here,

00:21:23.810 --> 00:21:25.430
the moderators are trying
to make it look like

00:21:25.430 --> 00:21:27.580
they're taking steps
to turn away those

00:21:27.580 --> 00:21:29.280
who might be very prone to being

00:21:29.280 --> 00:21:31.230
manipulated by others on the forum.

00:21:31.230 --> 00:21:32.630
To give a famous example,

00:21:32.630 --> 00:21:34.780
in the state of Georgia in 2006,

00:21:34.780 --> 00:21:36.530
a man named Roberto Rocha,

00:21:36.530 --> 00:21:38.560
a 20 year old who
worked as a landscaper,

00:21:38.560 --> 00:21:39.650
was coerced by police

00:21:39.650 --> 00:21:41.460
into giving a false
confession for murder.

00:21:41.710 --> 00:21:43.410
A murder it was later revealed

00:21:43.410 --> 00:21:44.870
