00:22:05.840 --> 00:22:06.750
no problem.

00:22:06.960 --> 00:22:09.530
But apart from disabilities
that affect comprehension,

00:22:09.530 --> 00:22:12.110
there are all kinds of other
vulnerable people out there.

00:22:12.110 --> 00:22:12.910
For example,

00:22:12.910 --> 00:22:14.840
those who suffer from
a form of psychosis,

00:22:14.840 --> 00:22:17.580
like the condition currently
defined as schizophrenia.

00:22:17.580 --> 00:22:19.130
A person with this condition

00:22:19.130 --> 00:22:20.870
in the middle of a psychotic episode

00:22:20.870 --> 00:22:23.770
might be highly susceptible to
suggestion and encouragement

00:22:23.770 --> 00:22:24.980
during that episode.

00:22:25.390 --> 00:22:27.130
So let's now ask the question:

00:22:27.130 --> 00:22:29.120
Does this forum take
appropriate steps

00:22:29.140 --> 00:22:31.470
to protect those who are
vulnerable to coercion?

00:22:32.810 --> 00:22:33.480
No.

00:22:33.480 --> 00:22:36.050
It's difficult to imagine a
