00:32:22.210 --> 00:32:23.610
So, to the next question:

00:32:23.610 --> 00:32:25.280
How is this site still up?

00:32:25.280 --> 00:32:27.900
And why do search engines
like Google still index it?

00:32:28.240 --> 00:32:29.320
Well, at present,

00:32:29.320 --> 00:32:31.560
neither are legally liable
for their content.

00:32:31.560 --> 00:32:32.900
It's protection afforded by

00:32:32.900 --> 00:32:36.370
Section 230 of Title 47 of
the United States Code,

00:32:36.370 --> 00:32:37.510
which shields platforms

00:32:37.510 --> 00:32:39.880
like Google or Facebook
or any other site

00:32:39.880 --> 00:32:41.110
for being held liable

00:32:41.110 --> 00:32:42.960
for the content published
by their users.

00:32:43.360 --> 00:32:44.640
It's a very important law,

00:32:44.640 --> 00:32:45.670
and, many argue,

00:32:45.670 --> 00:32:47.270
vital to the ability of the internet

00:32:47.270 --> 00:32:48.750
to function as we know it today.

00:32:49.170 --> 00:32:51.960
Trying to discuss the pros
and cons of Section 230 here

00:32:51.960 --> 00:32:54.650
would take us way too far from
the main point of this video.

00:32:54.650 --> 00:32:55.730
Suffice it to say

00:32:55.730 --> 00:32:58.030
that amending it is,
in practical terms,

00:32:58.030 --> 00:32:59.250
incredibly difficult,

00:32:59.620 --> 00:33:01.978
and doing so would not be
without negative consequences.

00:33:02.240 --> 00:33:02.860
However,

00:33:02.860 --> 00:33:05.420
expect to be hearing a lot
about this over the coming year,

00:33:05.420 --> 00:33:07.140
since there are already
two cases being

00:33:07.140 --> 00:33:09.420
considered by the
Supreme Court right now

00:33:09.420 --> 00:33:11.310
that revolve around Section 230.

00:33:11.310 --> 00:33:12.830
And there are more coming after that.

00:33:12.830 --> 00:33:14.520
I've put some useful
links in the description

00:33:14.520 --> 00:33:15.940
for those who want to learn more.

00:33:15.940 --> 00:33:16.580
Anyway,

00:33:16.580 --> 00:33:19.330
although it's not illegal
for Google to index SS,

00:33:19.330 --> 00:33:21.900
that's not to say they won't bow
to pressure from their users,

00:33:22.200 --> 00:33:22.900
us.

00:33:22.900 --> 00:33:24.370
As long as we shout loudly enough,

00:33:24.770 --> 00:33:27.440
